arStrings.szText: Well well! Someone let you outta yer cage did they, rat? Suppose you learned your lesson?
Extremely pleased with yourself. You're talking down to a weasel-y subordinate who had his punishment coming.
Aye! I know I did wrong, but I brought you the troublemaker who wrecked our camp! A little gift, wrapped up nice!
Nervous but trying to put on an air of confidence. Talking to The Boss, and trying to ingratiate yourself to them.
